    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic, well-maintained ride! It\u2019s in great shape and has clearly been cared for, offering a smooth drive and a clean, inviting interior. While it shows a few signs of careful use, it\u2019s a solid, reliable choice that looks sharp and is ready for many more miles of adventure!",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a functional, budget-friendly option for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are operational, though you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a bit of hesitation during cold starts. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, small dents, and some fading paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat. While it remains a reliable daily driver for now, it will eventually benefit from some cosmetic touch-ups and preventative mechanical maintenance to keep it running smoothly.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The engine and transmission operate like new with no mechanical issues. Both the exterior and interior are pristine, showing no signs of wear, damage, or aging.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
